    <item>
      <title>bug in widget.tpl</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/plupload/forum/general/bug_in_widget_tpl</link>
      <description>In plupload/design/standard/templates/widget.tpl there's a bug with the upload url that is passed to the upload runtime.&#13;
&#13;
The uploading url should be changed form this:&#13;
&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
{'plupload/upload'|ezroot(single)}&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
to this:&#13;
&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
{concat('plupload/upload/',$parentNodeID)|ezurl()}&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
So that the url of the current siteacces is used (i.e. admin), and not the url of the default siteaccess.&#13;
&#13;
</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Mavko Žmak - Žmale)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/plupload/forum/general/bug_in_widget_tpl</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Oct 2010 20:32:30 +0000</pubDate>
    </item>
